---
title: Tex-Mex BBQ Chicken Quesadillas with Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Baking quesadillas in the oven is a revelation. No more waiting for them to fry in batches and, while they're baking, you have time to make charred corn salsa, which is the perfect finishing touch on these tangy BBQ chicken quesadillas. Welcome to easy street, Tex Mex style!
